abstract: The partnership announcement with I.B.M. is a sign that Google may be getting its act together in the health care industry.
snippet: The partnership announcement with I.B.M. is a sign that Google may be getting its act together in the health care industry.
lead_paragraph: A joint Google-I.B.M. announcement on Wednesday night about software to link medical devices to Google’s personal health records, on its face, isn’t much of an announcement.
